body:
Someone dodges, my client freezes, then after about 45 seconds I'm sent back to the screen saying I neglected to accept the game. Then I am moved to the back of the queue EVERY TIME someone dodges. It's really kind of annoying considering I have to wait an unnecessary amount of time just to get into a game when one person dodges. (5 min queue, 5 min champ select, dodge, 5 min queue, 5 min champ select.... if dodge repeat....)

Seriously. Please. Help. This is annoying.

{{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}}
